  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/laptops/\" rel=\"tag\">膝上电脑</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/04/18/you-might-be-able-to-unlock-your-next-chromebook-with-your-smart\"><img alt=\"SONY DSC\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/7fc3da37644acd45f7c5668a8f8c629a/200045320/DSC00015.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n忘记你 <a href=\"http://chinese.engadget.com/tag/Chromebook/\">Chromebook</a> 的密码？嗯... 如果支援手机解锁功能，未来也许你将不再需要去记下那一大堆的麻烦密码了呢。根据 Google Chrome OS dev channel 的消息，以后他们将会为使用者提供手机接近笔电范围内的立即解锁功能：Easy Unlock。目前这项功能还尚未成真，不过这其实也不算是太新鲜的功能了 -- 之前就已经有开发团队推出了敲敲 iPhone 便可解锁 Mac 的有趣功能，跳转以后可以看看，也许我们可以期待未来的 Chromebook 会有更炫的呈现方式？<p><br /><p class=\"continueReading\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/04/18/you-might-be-able-to-unlock-your-next-chromebook-with-your-smart/\" rel=\"bookmark\">继续阅读全文 <em>次世代 Chromebook 将支援手机解锁？</em></a></p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/04/18/you-might-be-able-to-unlock-your-next-chromebook-with-your-smart/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20871657/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/04/18/you-might-be-able-to-unlock-your-next-chromebook-with-your-smart/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
